            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Venditio unius <rs key="#Petiae">petiê terrê</rs> positê in loco vocatur
                            <placeName key="#Petiae">Musilina a Padesmo</placeName>, facta a
                                <persName><name ref="Sigebrandus">Sisprando</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Sergius">Sergii</name></persName> favore
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannis</name></persName> et uxoris
                        eius. Actum in <placeName ref="#places/3539" key="#Curtes"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2450">Curte
                        Conca</geogName></placeName>. Rog. <persName key="#Notary"><name
                                ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs>. Anno <persName key="#Popes"
                            ref="#people/1636">Gregorii</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">papê</rs> I et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/7">Ottonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatoris</rs> I, 13 ianuarii, indictione X.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
